<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title the Add Button
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css")
  body

    h1.intro the Add Button
      small css animation version

    - var icons = ['💿', '☸', '❤', '🌏'];

    .box
      input.fab-checkbox.sr-only#fab-checkbox(type="checkbox", checked)
      .fab
        - each $, i in Array(4)
          label(for="fab-checkbox", data-icon=icons[i]).fab__item
        label(for="fab-checkbox").fab__cross

    blockquote.info
      | inspired from 
      a(href="https://dribbble.com/shots/1958250-GIF-for-the-Add-Button") GIF for the Add Button
      |  by 
      a(href="https://dribbble.com/SergeyValiukh") Sergey Valiukh
